20-years and made Oni, and the first 3 Halos. This guy is old and kind of legendary. Or at least a neat antique gaming fixture.

Also I’m a little annoyed I don’t get a shield with all the cool things I’ve worked on, from my job.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/b53bGqR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BrazilianThunderPanda]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Can confirm except for the coasties</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wD9P57m</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/72DXtCk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wD9P57m</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[roaduardo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A good outcome from a bad situation</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/m7jJTU9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NqFfFZk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We had to move cross country. Due to the pandemic there was simply no way to get him across the country by airplane or professional pet mover short of paying absurd sums of money and drastically altering our already complex travel arrangements. Our only choice was to have him in the carrier the entire six day long drive. Due to his health problems and serious anxiety that was considered a non starter, he wouldn’t survive the rigors of the journey. 

So, with heavy hearts we sent him to a cat rescue that specializes in kitties with behavior and health problems, of which he had both. 

We reached out to them recently, a year later, and found out they matched him with an elderly widow who by all accounts takes good care of him and treats him like a prince. Makes me happy.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/m7jJTU9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordOfZajo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They Told Her She Could, Then Arrested Her for Doing it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vtrWr3Y</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vf8Fl6s.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/apr/22/pamela-moses-prosecutor-drops-charges-memphis-tennessee

